Usage: ON [+|-|^]MAIL_IRC [-|^]<nicknames> [action]
  This is activated whenever you receive irc mail.
  The parameters for the action are as follows:
    $0    nickname of person who sent the mail
    $1    The user@hostname of the person who sent the mail
    $2    The mail flags (see HELP MAIL FLAGS)
    $3-8  The time the mail was queued.
    $9    The server from which the mail was queued
    $10-  The message itself

